# shor21_a2 — 완전 Shor 주기발견 (N=21, a=2). 12q: c0..c6(counting 7) | w0..w4(work 5).
# N=21≠2^k-1 → ×2 mod21이 진짜 carry/reduction(cmul2/4/16_mod21, reversible synthesis). N=15 특수성 완전 탈피.
# H^7 · controlled-U^{2^j}(c_j, U=×2, powers 16/4/16/4/16/4/2) · iQFT7. work=|1>.
# 판독: counting/128 연속분수 → r=6 → gcd(2^3±1,21)=7,3 → 21=3×7 (확률적, P(r=6)≈0.23, t=7≥2r²).
